children.text: The Hebel wall system has not been provided with vertical control joints for expansion and contraction at the external corner in this area, which could cause failure of the system.
The Hebel Power Panel external wall design and installation instructions state in section 3.5.7 Control Joints, that
â€˜The following information provides the necessary rules for control jointing when installing the Hebel PowerPanelXL External Wall System;
- Vertical control joints required at external and internal corners.'
This required control joint must be properly installed to prevent failure of the Hebel system, prior to works in this area proceeding any further.
